data.description: This jewel is located in the Bradbury Court neighborhood of San Antonio, conveniently located off of FM 78, 5 miles to Randolph Air Force Base, and 6 miles to Fort Sam Houston, near I35 for a quick commute to work or shop. This amazing home includes 3 great size bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Home features living area, dining area and primary room with walk-in closet, and separate shower. The kitchen features plenty of cabinets and countertops with beautiful tile backsplash. Within a short distance to HEB, IKIA, The Forum with lots of stores and restaurants including Home Depot, Best Buy, and much more. Gather the family for an amazing BBQ in the covered patio and create memories that will last a life time. (This home can be purchased with an assumable mortgage with an interest rate of 2.9%) Don't wait, as you won't be able to get this interest rate even through a builder!
